<p>Cory Doctorow explains the problems in Bluesky&rsquo;s privacy policy:</p>
<blockquote class="quoteback" data-author="pluralistic.net" data-avatar="![img](https://micro.blog/pluralistic.net/avatar.jpg)" cite="https://pluralistic.net/2025/08/15/dogs-breakfast/">
